      "relevant_text_blocks": [
        "Alliance Duel (VS) - Last War: Survival Game Wiki Skip to content Menu Menu Home",
        "The Alliance Duel, also called Alliance VS, is an event in Last War Survival where two alliances face off by completing tasks to earn points. The alliance that earns the most points during the event wins.",
        "This event lasts for over a week, with a new set of tasks each day that alliance members can complete to help their alliance earn points.",
        "Participation Requirements",
        "To participate in the Alliance VS event, players must meet the following requirements:",
        "You must belong to an eligible alliance.",
        "Alliances must have at least 20 members to join the event.",
        "Only the top 32 alliances in the Warzone (server) can participate.",
        "The event is divided into six themes, each offering different “Winning Points”:",
        "The “Winning Points” represent how many points an alliance can earn each day. For example, the first day’s theme offers 1 point, while the last day provides 4 points. The alliance with the most Winning Points at the end of the event is declared the winner.",
        "Here are the base points you can earn from each theme, without applying the perks from “Alliance VS” research:",
        "Day 1: Radar Training",
        "Day 2: Base Expansion",
        "Day 3: Age of Science",
        "Day 5: Total Mobilization",
        "Every Level 1 Unit killed from rival alliance – 10 points",
        "Every Level 2 Unit killed from rival alliance – 15 points",
        "Every Level 3 Unit killed from rival alliance – 20 points"
      ],
